          <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2 animate-pulse" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
          </svg>
          Tecnología de Vanguardia
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6 leading-tight">
          Sistema Diseñado para 
          <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-600 via-sky-400 to-sky-500 animate-gradient">
            Profesionales
          </span>
        </h2>

        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          Nuestra plataforma combina facilidad de uso con características avanzadas, 
          permitiendo que los profesionales de la salud se concentren en lo más importante: sus pacientes.
        </p>

        <!-- Enhanced feature cards with better hover effects -->
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-4 group hover:bg-white hover:shadow-lg hover:border-primary-100 border border-transparent rounded-xl p-4 transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-100 to-primary-200 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 group-hover:animate-pulse" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
